fcitx5-vnkey (0.0.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Telex input method with full NFC precomposed tone output.
  * Standalone C++23 engine core (libvietcore) with unit test suite.
  * Fcitx5 addon layer: preedit, per-context state, commit-with-space,
    Enter/Tab key forwarding.

